            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1894-12-17T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1894-12-17T00:00:00-05:00" n="130" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d130">
                <head>No. 130.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Baker</persName>
                            to Mr. <persName type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of
                                    the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">La
                                Libertad</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-12-17">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 17,
                            1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mosquito Indians have surrendered their rights under the treaty of 1860 and
                        been incorporated with Nicaragua.</p>
            </div>
